Class Robot

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.princesslana.eriscasper.api.robot.Robot
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Bot, Function<BotContext,Completable>

    public class Robot
extends java.lang.Object
implements Bot
    Robot presents an API that allows execution of callbacks when messages matching regexes are received.

      • respond

        public void respond(java.util.regex.Pattern regex,
                    Function<RobotContext,Completable> f)
        Checks all messages sent directly to the Robot against the provided regex. Executes the provided function when there is a match.

        Messages are considered to be directed at the Robot if they begin with "+", the username of the bot account, or a mention of the bot account.

        Parameters:
        regex - regex to match
        f - function to execute when matched
